This Android app is a port of the old Tyrian vertical shoot-em-up, originally
written in TurboPascal for DOS.
This project is licensed under GPLv2, for further licensing information see the
LICENSE file.

Build Instructions:
Import project into Eclipse, since I have not created Ant makefiles for this project.
For help building the opentyrian C library, please consult the INSTALL file. 

Known Issues:
None yet.

This project uses opentyrian from http://code.google.com/p/opentyrian
originally ported from TurboPascal by the opentyrian team
